Discworld concepts help
hitpoints

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
hit points - how much damage you can take.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Hit points determine how much damage you can take before you die.  The
number of hit points you have is dependant on your stats (primarily
Con) and your level in other.health.

Hit points regenerate automatically with time.  There are also a
variety of other ways to get healed.

You can use the monitor command to help keep track of your current hit points.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
combat, wimpy, monitor.
.EP
